high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the fridge, then hang a left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the large golden spoon with a blue handle off of the counter in front of the sink.
Put the golden spoon in the sink and turn on the water, after a couple seconds turn the water off and remove the now clean golden spoon.
Turn around and walk over to the left side of the kitchen island.
Put the clean golden spoon on the kitchen island.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean large golden spoon on the kitchen island.

high_descs: Walk to the kitchen counter behind you.
Grab a ladle off the counter.
Place the ladle inside the sink, rinse it, then grab the ladle again.
Walk to the kitchen table on the salt and pepper shakers' side.
Place the ladle on the table.
anns.task_desc: Clean a ladle and place it on a table.

high_descs: turn left, turn left ,walk to the sink
grab the spoon by the sink
walk towards the sink a little
put the spoon in the sink, wash the spoon with water,take the spoon out
turn around, walk to the kitchen island
put the spoon on the kitchen island
anns.task_desc: wash the spoon by the sink, put it on the kitchen island
